    {
      "text": "Bomberman Land Touch! is a puzzle video game developed by Hudson Soft for the Nintendo DS. The game was first released in Japan and North America in 2006. Part of the Bomberman franchise,  Touch! is the fourth game in the Bomberman Land series and its first to be released outside Japan.",
